7:["$","article",null,{"className":"min-h-screen bg-white","children":["$","div",null,{"className":"max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12","children":[["$","header",null,{"className":"mb-8","children":[["$","h1",null,{"className":"text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4","children":"How can ISO 45001 certification benefit supply chain globally?"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"flex items-center gap-4 text-gray-600","children":[["$","time",null,{"dateTime":"2026-01-02T06:31:23+00:00","children":"January 2, 2026"}],["$","span",null,{"className":"inline-block px-3 py-1 bg-blue-100 text-blue-800 rounded-full text-sm","children":"general"}]]}]]}],null,["$","div",null,{"className":"mb-8 p-4 bg-gray-50 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-blue-500","children":["$","p",null,{"className":"text-gray-700 italic","children":"Given the worldwide nature of business these days and that several businesses operate globally, this ISO certification standard additionally has tangible"}]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"prose prose-lg max-w-none mb-8 text-gray-700 leading-relaxed","children":[["$","p","0",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"How can ISO 45001 certification benefit supply chain globally?"}],["$","p","1",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"When ISO 45001 certification was published in March 2018, ISO certification consultants and representative from over seventy countries had contributed to the final draft. This implies that ISO 45001 standard which replaced OHSAS 18001, would become one amongst the most-used standards within the ISO suite. Given the worldwide nature of business these days and that several businesses operate globally, this ISO certification standard additionally has tangible advantages for organizations that have, or are a part of international supply chains."}],["$","p","2",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"So, what are these advantages, and the way do the principles of ISO 45001 improve your international supply chain?"}],["$","p","3",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Sole benefits of Implementing ISO 45001 certification"}],["$","p","4",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"One of the numerous benefits of ISO 45001 is that the adoption of Annex SL allowed this ISO standard to be integrated with different standards, corresponding to ISO 9001 and ISO 14001, amongst others, as we tend to examined within the previous article the way to integrate ISO 45001 with ISO 9001 and ISO 14001. Therefore, if you're implementing ISO 45001 certification within a combined management system, you must identify your environmental, quality, and health and safety objectives and processes easier to combine; however even implementation of ISO 45001 alone, the advantages to your international supply chain will be more than beneficial in one ways."}],["$","p","5",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"How can ISO 45001 certification improve business consistency of a global supply chain?"}],["$","p","6",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"The success of your global supply chain, like several smaller business unit, depends on achieving objectives and satisfying customers. To do this, a worldwide business must be able to make sure that key workers with key skills are within the right place at the right time. ISO 45001, with its objective of maintaining worker health, safety and well-being, will facilitate accomplish this, particularly if enforced systematically throughout a whole international supply chain."}],"$L10","$L11","$L12","$L13","$L14","$L15","$L16","$L17","$L18","$L19","$L1a"]}],"$L1b"]}]}]
